{"tid":2299601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周五財會擬抽議程 讓路明日大嶼撥款","createTime":"2020-11-25T02:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T02:41:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f10addf5278a7f26cec602e8296367df62b42cc","tid":2299601,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/SDLNWAARGZDLLMVTBGPFJ7VEG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FSDLNWAARGZDLLMVTBGPFJ7VEG4%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=bed4e39e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FSDLNWAARGZDLLMVTBGPFJ7VEG4%2F&h=bfb9fa9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/SDLNWAARGZDLLMVTBGPFJ7VEG4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n周五財會擬抽議程 讓路明日大嶼撥款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PAo9ClmULr5HpGdYJysN_FbtbNs=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IUBQSTC46ZGONHKPLZQ7PPVWPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPAo9ClmULr5HpGdYJysN_FbtbNs%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIUBQSTC46ZGONHKPLZQ7PPVWPY.jpg&h=6f35041d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府將向立法會申請5.5億交椅洲填海前期研究撥款。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥今日發表新一份《施政報告》，房屋及土地議題將續成重點，消息指《施政報告》將觸及爭議不斷的明日大嶼計劃，料交代最新進展，更有消息指政府有意將明日大嶼前期研究撥款申請，提前在《施政報告》後、本周五財委會審議，並預料經過幾次會議後便「火速」表決通過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料建制派極速通過<br />\n<br />\n《施政報告》料交代多項增加土地及房屋供應政策，料政府將續推展涉1,700公頃土地的明日大嶼計劃。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n發展局2018年初步估算明日大嶼造價達6,240億元，惹社會譁然。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n惟民主黨及公民黨日前公佈民調，指有五成半受訪者不支持明日大嶼，支持僅27％；調查更顯示，連自稱建制派支持者的受訪者，支持明日大嶼亦未能過半。但有泛民議員預料，現無議員拉布抵抗惡法，建制派將會極速通過撥款，研究工作過後，明日大嶼工程亦將暢通無阻地進行。"},{"pid":"3b7c1fba75dd1dfeb222ca43082843c2b619d1a3","tid":2299601,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"襯議會無乜人 一炮過洗哂去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}